room_title: Escape room "Poison Ivy" by Escape Room NJ in New York
room_description: Poison Ivy has enticed you into her Funhouse with an invitation to a little get together! Before long you realize there is something not quite right going on and you are starting to feel light headed. You have 60 Minutes to figure out all of her many riddles lewd puzzles and questionable mental challenges before the lethal gas fills the room and you are powerless against Poison Ivy!
